Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 7/14/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio discussing toxic tendencies, if cops can smoke weed, a selfie in a volcano, and Styles P police encounter.

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
